column2: select top # za.z, za.ra, za.dec, za.bestObjID, po.objID, po.type, po.flags, po.ra, po.dec from specObj za join PhotoObjAll po ON (po.objID = za.bestObjID) join Photoz zp on (zp.objID = za.bestObjID) join galSpecInfo zi on (zi.SpecObjID = za.specObjID) where za.class = # and za.z > # and za.zWarning = #
